source/Ondo_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ondo_State\"}, {\"begin\": 1267, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasarawa_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.971268913310738e-38, \"text\": \"Nasarawa\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasarawa_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasarawa_State\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic Day is a special day to come together, move together, and learn about the Olympic values,\\\" said Abdul Ibrahim, the Chairman of the NOC Sport For All Commission.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_Johor\", \"score\": 0.9851272118803741, \"rank\": 0.007298523342700069, \"text\": \"Ibrahim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_Johor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_Johor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We encourage everyone to participate and experience the joy that only sport can bring.\\\"\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ballon d'Or: Benzema chooses player to win award this season  Transfer: It will be difficult for me to play with Neymar again - Messi  NOC mourns former Kano Pillars Chairman  NOC planning to impose illegal SOC in Kogi - NMA cries out  AFCON 2023: NOC urges Super Eagles to go for ultimate prize  Paris Olympics: NOC sets target for athletes, administrators  NOC chairman seeks stakeholders' support for 2024 Olympics, others  NOC congratulates Tobi Amusan on Diamond League victory  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Benzema\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Benzema\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour